Class StorageKeyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.seanchenxi.gwt.storage.client.StorageKeyFactory

  • public class StorageKeyFactory
extends Object
    Storage Key Factory

    Choose type correspond method for all primitive type values' key,
    Use serializableKey(String) for Serializable object type Use isSerializableKey(String) for IsSerializable object type
